<h4>Shows render overhead (with complex component)</h4>

This section shows the overhead of bind. We have @Foo.N elements (just the first is displayed, but the others will still be consume time, if rendered)

@foreach (var element in Elements)
{
    var first = Elements.First();
    <BindToComplex @bind-Value="@element.Value" Show="@(element == first)" />
}
<hr />
@code {
    private List<Foo> Elements = Enumerable.Range(0, Foo.N).Select(i => new Foo { Value = i }).ToList();
}